</li></ul></li><li> Most of the ambience in <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/TwistedMetalBlack" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/TwistedMetalBlack">Twisted Metal: Black</a></em> fits this trope, but <a class="urllink" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E_GqM98ymcg">Snowy Fields<img src="https://static.tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pub/external_link.gif" height="12" width="12" style="border:none;"></a> is the epitome of terrifying drone.
